### =====================================================
### Neon Ark Creature Management System
### API Route Testing
### =====================================================

### =====================================================
### 1. Get All Creatures
### =====================================================

GET http://localhost:8081/api/creatures


### =====================================================
### 2. Get Creature By ID
### =====================================================

GET http://localhost:8081/api/creatures/1


### =====================================================
### 3. Create Creature
### =====================================================

POST http://localhost:8081/api/creatures
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Drako",
  "species": "Inferno Wyvern",
  "dangerLevel": "HIGH",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "notes": "Extremely aggressive near containment walls.",
  "habitatId": 1
}


### =====================================================
### 4. Rename Creature
### =====================================================

PUT http://localhost:8081/api/creatures/1/name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newName": "Nyx Prime"
}


### =====================================================
### 5. Soft Delete Creature
### =====================================================

DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/creatures/4


### =====================================================
### 6. Get Creature Observations
### =====================================================

GET http://localhost:8081/api/creatures/1/observations


### =====================================================
### 7. Find Feedings By Time
### =====================================================

GET http://localhost:8081/api/feedings?time=08:00


### =====================================================
### 8. Get Admin Users
### =====================================================

GET http://localhost:8081/api/admin/users


### =====================================================
### 9. Validation Test - Invalid Creature ID
### =====================================================

GET http://localhost:8081/api/creatures/-1


### =====================================================
### 10. Conflict Test - Duplicate Creature Name
### =====================================================

POST http://localhost:8081/api/creatures
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nyx Prime",
  "species": "Void Panther",
  "dangerLevel": "HIGH",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "notes": "Duplicate test case.",
  "habitatId": 1
}


### =====================================================
### 11. Bad Request Test - Invalid Feeding Time
### =====================================================

GET http://localhost:8081/api/feedings?time=invalid